  "detailed_description": "CRUX is a fast-paced single player arena shooter roguelike inspired by the refined mechanics and the drive to mastery of old school boomer shooter of the 90s and the replayability and powerful abilities of roguelike action games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/34c50a2cdf1237e8603004f965da22b7.poster.avif?t=1709799509\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/34c50a2cdf1237e8603004f965da22b7.webm?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/34c50a2cdf1237e8603004f965da22b7.mp4?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In CRUX you play as a cultist warrior of the blood gods, trained from childhood to undertake the trials of the CRUX. The trials consist of 13 arenas across 5 worlds, where you'll face hordes of demons native to that world. Survive the hordes to earn the right to face the Guardian of the Arena, boss fights unique to each arena that will test your skills with movement, weapons, controlling the arena.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/f5fe759ac3d224b2fa2de9b5c4a2a11b.poster.avif?t=1709799509\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/f5fe759ac3d224b2fa2de9b5c4a2a11b.webm?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/f5fe759ac3d224b2fa2de9b5c4a2a11b.mp4?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The blood gods watch your step, and for every arena they will bless you with a selection of magic abilities to increase your power. With a selection of over 100 abilities you will have the opportunity to customize your gameplay to suit your playstyle. Whether you want to bust your foes' skulls with the Skullcrusher, chain lightning magic, steal their lifeforce (or much more!), the choice is yours!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/daaeec276873d60d69eab414f945c224.poster.avif?t=1709799509\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/daaeec276873d60d69eab414f945c224.webm?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/daaeec276873d60d69eab414f945c224.mp4?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Successfully beating all the arenas will land you a spot in the leaderboards. But the true champion is the fastest one, so customize your build and go again to try and get to the top spot!",
  "about_the_game": "CRUX is a fast-paced single player arena shooter roguelike inspired by the refined mechanics and the drive to mastery of old school boomer shooter of the 90s and the replayability and powerful abilities of roguelike action games.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/34c50a2cdf1237e8603004f965da22b7.poster.avif?t=1709799509\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/34c50a2cdf1237e8603004f965da22b7.webm?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/34c50a2cdf1237e8603004f965da22b7.mp4?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In CRUX you play as a cultist warrior of the blood gods, trained from childhood to undertake the trials of the CRUX. The trials consist of 13 arenas across 5 worlds, where you'll face hordes of demons native to that world. Survive the hordes to earn the right to face the Guardian of the Arena, boss fights unique to each arena that will test your skills with movement, weapons, controlling the arena.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/f5fe759ac3d224b2fa2de9b5c4a2a11b.poster.avif?t=1709799509\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/f5fe759ac3d224b2fa2de9b5c4a2a11b.webm?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/f5fe759ac3d224b2fa2de9b5c4a2a11b.mp4?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The blood gods watch your step, and for every arena they will bless you with a selection of magic abilities to increase your power. With a selection of over 100 abilities you will have the opportunity to customize your gameplay to suit your playstyle. Whether you want to bust your foes' skulls with the Skullcrusher, chain lightning magic, steal their lifeforce (or much more!), the choice is yours!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/daaeec276873d60d69eab414f945c224.poster.avif?t=1709799509\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/daaeec276873d60d69eab414f945c224.webm?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2293200/extras/daaeec276873d60d69eab414f945c224.mp4?t=1709799509\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Successfully beating all the arenas will land you a spot in the leaderboards. But the true champion is the fastest one, so customize your build and go again to try and get to the top spot!",
